01 - RIP</span><hr size=1> Let us never forget this great tragedy to human life, and civilisation as a whole.<br>
<br>
What happened nearly 1 year ago shows us what is capable in the name of 'fundamentalism'.<br>
Catastrophe has a new edge. What we thought as morally impossible; had no boundaries for these people. The world has never been the same since, and i hope the change is for the better.<br>
I am not old or experienced enough to write an ode which is worth the tragedy, or as a memory for all the firefighters, civilians and others that died in the incident.<br>
All i want to say is that i remember these people, and i hope they rest in peace.<br>
<br>
In memory of all the people involved in the Manhatten Island tragedy.<br>
